// TEST: ML Equiv Certified Calls Certified
import ml as ml
// ============================================================================
// Composition: a certified function may call another certified function of
// the SAME group; the callee's declared signature is trusted (its own body
// was judged). Same-spec addition scales through.
// ============================================================================
let static S = [(0, 0, 1), (1, 1, 1)]
function double(x: Array<Float like IrrepsIdx<S>>) where ml.equiv(O3) -> Array<Float like IrrepsIdx<S>> =
  x + x
function quad(x: Array<Float like IrrepsIdx<S>>) where ml.equiv(O3) -> Array<Float like IrrepsIdx<S>> =
  double(double(x))
let out = quad([1.0, 2.0, 3.0, 4.0])
// EXPECT: out = [4.0, 8.0, 12.0, 16.0]
